zornmesh 0.1.0
Local-first agent mesh coordination.

Usage: zornmesh [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  daemon   Start or inspect the local zornmesh daemon
  agents   List and inspect registered agents
  doctor   Run first-day local mesh diagnostics
  stdio    Bridge an MCP-compatible host over stdio
  inspect  Inspect persisted messages, dead letters, audit entries, and metadata
  trace    Reconstruct conversation timelines by correlation ID
  tail     Live-tail envelope flow by subject pattern
  replay   Redeliver a previously sent envelope by message ID
  retention Plan retention purges and surface retention gaps
  audit    Verify the audit log hash chain offline
  release  Verify release signatures and inspect SBOM evidence
  compliance  Audit compliance traceability fields on evidence records
  completion  Generate shell completions
  help     Print command help

Options:
      --config <PATH>   Read CLI defaults from a key=value config file
      --socket <PATH>   Override the local daemon socket path
      --output <FORMAT> Select human, json, or ndjson output
      --non-interactive Fail fast instead of prompting
  -h, --help            Print help
  -V, --version         Print version

Exit codes:
  64  user error or unsupported CLI input
  65  validation failure
  66  not found
  69  daemon unreachable
  74  daemon I/O failure
  75  temporary unavailable or daemon already running
  77  permission denied or unsafe local trust
